269
00:28:26,599 --> 00:28:31,220
[SPEAKER_02] zato jer mi nismo baš tipični,

270
00:28:31,220 --> 00:28:34,640
[SPEAKER_02] opet da se krivo ne izrazim,

271
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:38,779
[SPEAKER_02] ali nemamo taj 9 do 5 radno vrijeme

272
00:28:38,779 --> 00:28:40,579
