274
00:28:42,779 --> 00:28:45,420
[SPEAKER_02] i onda provodimo tih par nekih sati zajedno.

275
00:28:45,420 --> 00:28:50,160
[SPEAKER_02] Ali, kako to balansiramo?

276
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:54,319
[SPEAKER_02] Pa tak, balansiramo dosta dobro,

277
00:28:54,319 --> 00:28:58,200
[SPEAKER_02] ali nemam sad tu neke upute u biti.

278
00:28:58,200 --> 00:29:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] Mi samo živimo svoj život.

279
00:29:00,559 --> 00:29:02,799
[SPEAKER_02] Ne znam kako to rekao.

280
00:29:02,799 --> 00:29:03,339
[SPEAKER_02] Pa to je lijepo.

281
00:29:03,339 --> 00:29:04,759
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, imam ja jedan tvoj citat.

282
00:29:04,759 --> 00:29:07,680
[SPEAKER_01] Živim i radim u svom tempu.

283
00:29:07,680 --> 00:29:09,180
[SPEAKER_01] Meni se to baš svidjelo.

284
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:11,920
[SPEAKER_01] kao sad je to tako,

285
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:13,059
