286
00:29:13,059 --> 00:29:14,559
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi li uvijek mogla živjeti u svom tempu?

287
00:29:14,559 --> 00:29:15,200
[SPEAKER_02] Pa nije, nije.

288
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:16,440
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim, to sad mogu reći,

289
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:18,660
[SPEAKER_02] zato jer radim posao

290
00:29:18,660 --> 00:29:20,740
[SPEAKER_02] koji sam si sama stvorila,

291
00:29:20,740 --> 00:29:21,599
[SPEAKER_02] to jest pokrenula,

292
00:29:21,599 --> 00:29:24,140
[SPEAKER_02] pa to onda mogu sad tako.

293
00:29:24,140 --> 00:29:25,960
[SPEAKER_02] To jednostavno znači da

294
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:28,660
[SPEAKER_02] ću si posao organizirati

295
00:29:28,660 --> 00:29:32,359
[SPEAKER_02] onoliko koliko ga mogu napraviti

296
00:29:32,359 --> 00:29:34,319
[SPEAKER_02] i koliko ga želim napraviti

297
00:29:34,319 --> 00:29:36,259
[SPEAKER_02] i koliko ga trebam napraviti.

298
00:29:36,259 --> 00:29:41,420
[SPEAKER_02] Ja organiziram radiojnice kod sebe doma.

299
00:29:41,420 --> 00:29:43,980
[SPEAKER_02] Jednostavno si organiziram termine

300
00:29:43,980 --> 00:29:45,299
[SPEAKER_02] koje meni odgovaraju.

301
00:29:45,299 --> 00:29:49,140
[SPEAKER_02] Neke suradnje koje imam preko društvenih mreža.

302
00:29:50,740 --> 00:29:54,420
[SPEAKER_02] Uzmem koliko ih mogu odraditi fizički.

303
00:29:54,420 --> 00:29:58,180
[SPEAKER_02] Ne želim si previše toga staviti na svoj tanjur.

304
00:29:58,180 --> 00:30:01,299
[SPEAKER_02] I tak jednostavno funkcioniram.

305
00:30:01,299 --> 00:30:03,759
[SPEAKER_02] I to je to.

306
00:30:03,759 --> 00:30:04,680
[SPEAKER_02] To je moj tempo.

307
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:09,220
[SPEAKER_02] Ako mi se, ne znam,

308
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:11,000
[SPEAKER_02] jedan dan ne da ništa raditi

309
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:13,480
[SPEAKER_02] i hoću gledat seriju na Netflixu,

310
00:30:13,480 --> 00:30:15,480
[SPEAKER_02] neću se osjećati loše zbog toga.

311
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:16,859
[SPEAKER_01] Kak si došla do toga

312
00:30:16,859 --> 00:30:18,799
[SPEAKER_01] da se ne osjećaš loše kad onak samostaniš?

313
00:30:18,799 --> 00:30:20,000
[SPEAKER_02] Pa zato jer ima trenutka

314
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:22,380
[SPEAKER_02] gdje sam baš ono, ne znam,

315
00:30:22,380 --> 00:30:25,220
[SPEAKER_02] ima perioda kad baš puno radim.

316
00:30:25,220 --> 00:30:27,700
[SPEAKER_02] Ali sam zato jer imam energije

317
00:30:27,700 --> 00:30:29,480
[SPEAKER_02] za to i mogu to odraditi.

318
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:32,539
[SPEAKER_02] Recimo, početkom ove godine

319
00:30:32,539 --> 00:30:34,839
[SPEAKER_02] sam otišla na turneju

320
00:30:34,839 --> 00:30:36,480
[SPEAKER_02] koju sam si sama organizirala

321
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:39,240
[SPEAKER_02] do Dubrovnika gdje sam imala dvije radionice.

322
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:45,240
[SPEAKER_02] U Splitu sam imala jednu radionicu,

323
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:46,900
[SPEAKER_02] u Makarskoj jednu radionicu.

324
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:48,619
[SPEAKER_02] pardon, na kraju ih je bilo pet,

325
00:30:48,619 --> 00:30:51,059
[SPEAKER_02] ali nešto, negdje sam pogubila nešto.

326
00:30:51,059 --> 00:30:53,359
[SPEAKER_02] Uglavnom ne, bile su tri radionice u Dubrovniku,

327
00:30:53,359 --> 00:30:55,799
[SPEAKER_02] jedna u Makarskoj, jedna u Splitu.

328
00:30:55,799 --> 00:30:58,720
[SPEAKER_02] I to je bilo pet radionica u pet dana.

329
00:30:58,720 --> 00:31:00,359
[SPEAKER_02] Nemoj Dubrovčane izgubiti.

330
00:31:00,359 --> 00:31:02,200
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, tamo sam bila tri dana.

331
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:03,359
[SPEAKER_02] Da, i bolje da jesi.

332
00:31:03,359 --> 00:31:05,980
[SPEAKER_02] Idem često tamo i volim iću Dubrovnik

333
00:31:05,980 --> 00:31:08,720
[SPEAKER_02] i opet ću ić, jer vole moje radionice

334
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:10,099
[SPEAKER_02] i volim ja iću Dubrovnik.

335
00:31:10,099 --> 00:31:12,579
